Better Homes and Gardens Real Estate Gary Greene -

data.description: Beautiful five-bedroom, four-bathroom, two-story home situated on a sizeable lot. This home features a spacious open floor plan with high ceilings, large kitchen with beautiful cabinetry, tiled backsplash, large island, stainless appliances and gorgeous wood flooring. Nice, covered patio to enjoy your backyard. Huge game room upstairs and office downstairs. Separate tub & shower in the primary and double vanity with a walk-in closet. 3-car garage. An added bonus is the clubhouse, community pool, park, and private boat launch to Lake Conroe located in the nearby sister community Water Crest on Lake Conroe.
